    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awaken in a forest, only to be rescued by a group of mysterious girls.<br>They are traveling in search of a certain monster.<br>You decide to join their journey and walk alongside them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ A Card Battle Where Your Hand Is the Resource</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/1edfbfdf261cc2c10c1f873c394ce773.poster.avif?t=1759175564\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/1edfbfdf261cc2c10c1f873c394ce773.webm?t=1759175564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/1edfbfdf261cc2c10c1f873c394ce773.mp4?t=1759175564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain new cards through battles and events to build your deck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To play a card, you must use the card to its right as the cost</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Careful hand management determines victory in this unique deck-building card game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Three Types of Cards for Strategic Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/1c3b37c895fdf7e071aa33eb8c3e11bc.avif?t=1759175564\" width=1376 height=472 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Attack Cards</strong>: Deal damage to enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defense Cards</strong>: Reduce damage taken on the next turn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special Cards</strong>: Effects such as drawing or swapping cards to change the tide of battle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Field Events</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/a45d039994786753e9e8a4962756054f.poster.avif?t=1759175564\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/a45d039994786753e9e8a4962756054f.webm?t=1759175564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/a45d039994786753e9e8a4962756054f.mp4?t=1759175564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various events occur along the journey. Your choices will shape the course of the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Bonus System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/8035fbddccdf28bf83251ae1d3457d97.poster.avif?t=1759175564\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/8035fbddccdf28bf83251ae1d3457d97.webm?t=1759175564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301870/extras/8035fbddccdf28bf83251ae1d3457d97.mp4?t=1759175564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn EXP as you progress through your adventure.<br>Spend EXP to gain bonuses for your next run, creating new strategies each time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play using <strong>only the mouse</strong> for simple and intuitive gameplay.</p>",
